sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  actor U as User
  participant APP as App
  participant BMS as BMS

  U->>APP: Open My Profile
  APP-->>U: Show Change default floor<br/>if is_fs_member = true

  U->>APP: Tap Change default floor

  APP->>BMS: GET /members/{memberId}?location_id={currentLocationId}
  BMS-->>APP: Return towers, defaultFloor, passes

  Note over APP: Read local locations.json<br/>Map locationId ↔ floorId

  APP-->>U: Show floor list<br/>with current default selected

  U->>APP: Select new floor
  APP-->>U: Show Continue button

  U->>APP: Tap Continue
  APP-->>U: Show confirmation modal

  alt User cancels
    U->>APP: Cancel
    APP-->>U: Back to floor selection
  else User confirms
    U->>APP: Confirm
    APP->>BMS: PUT /members/{memberId}<br/>{ default_floor: floorId }

    alt Update failed
      BMS-->>APP: Error / result = false
      APP-->>U: Show error announcement
    else Update success
      BMS-->>APP: result = true
      Note over APP: Update local default_floor<br/>floorId → locationId
      APP-->>U: Show success announcement
    end
  end
